0feedback%20about%20a%205-day%20RTO%20mandate%20%E2%80%94%20and%20much%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWorkers%20who%20aren't%20down%20can%20go%20elsewhere%2C%20Stankey%20signaled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20requirements%20dictated%20by%20this%20dynamic%20do%20not%20align%20to%20your%20personal%20desires%2C%20you%20have%20every%20right%20to%20find%20a%20career%20opportunity%20that%20is%20suitable%20to%20your%20aspirations%20and%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5dbe5c4-7dec-41e0-a25b-eba557730877%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGetting%20ahead%20in%20the%20new%20era%20of%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20ahead%20in%20your%20career%20or%20even%20just%20stay%20employed%20in%20this%20no-nonsense%20landscape%2C%20career%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20some%20workers%20will%20have%20to%20adapt.%20That%20can%20mean%20showing%20up%20in%20person%2C%20highlighting%20what%20you%20bring%20to%20the%20table%2C%20and%20expecting%20to%20hear%20fewer%20applause%20lines%20like%20%26quot%3Bwork-life%20balance%26quot%3B%20than%20only%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20spillover%20from%20home%20life%20to%20work%20life%20is%20not%20of%20concern%20to%20bosses%20these%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Yale%20University%20management%20professor%20Jeffrey%20Sonnenfeld.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20the%20time%20to%20talk%20about%20what%20makes%20your%20creature%20comforts%20so%20different%20from%20everybody%20else's%2C%20that%20somehow%20the%20company%20has%20to%20accommodate%20your%20needs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20companies%20that%20are%20doubling%20down%20on%20a%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-advice-documenting-success-wins-promotions-job-security-layoffs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehardcore%20work%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20even%20things%20like%20getting%20a%20dental%20cleaning%20during%20the%20workday%20may%20be%20more%20fraught.%20%26quot%3BCatering%20to%20convenience%20is%20not%20the%20driving%20force%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20Sonnenfeld%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStankey's%20remarks%20echo%20back-to-business%20messages%20from%20other%20CEOs.%20Jassy%20said%20last%20year%20that%20changes%2C%20including%20corporate%20workers%20being%20in%20the%20office%20more%20often%2C%20would%20help%20strengthen%20Amazon's%20culture.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternal-memo-meta-increases-employees-rated-below-expectations-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20raised%20performance%20expectations%2C%20while%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-performance-management-low-performers-country-club-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20appears%20to%20be%20dispensing%20with%20its%20%26quot%3Bcountry%20club%26quot%3B%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20company%20leaders%20are%20essentially%20saying%20is%20%26quot%3Beither%20you're%20fully%20aligned%20or%20you're%20disposable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Amanda%20Goodall%2C%20an%20independent%20provider%20of%20workforce%20intelligence%20for%20investors%20and%20executives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2219b6f2f3-028e-4021-ade0-c85385c69b45%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20job%20seekers%20should%20consider%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKnowing%20more%20about%20an%20organization's%20culture%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20for%20applicants%2C%20Jasmine%20Escalera%2C%20a%20career%20expert%20with%20MyPerfectResume%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20in%20an%20interview%20and%20notice%20a%20hiring%20manager%20emphasizing%20business%20imperatives%20and%20speaking%20less%20about%20topics%20like%20worker%20well-being%2C%20you%20can%20match%20their%20language%2C%20while%20still%20getting%20insights%20into%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20work%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFocus%20on%20business%20metrics%20and%20performance%20measures%2C%20said%20Escalera.%20For%20instance%2C%20that%20might%20mean%20asking%20how%20an%20emphasis%20on%20performance%20fits%20with%20employee%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2298b470a8-2403-49a3-97b1-d156999a4f8c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDeciding%20your%20priorities%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20workers%20might%20welcome%20leaders%20articulating%20a%20hardcore%20direction%20%E2%80%94%20either%20because%20the%20employees%20embrace%20that%20approach%20or%20because%20they%20appreciate%20candor%20from%20the%20top%20about%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20others%2C%20such%20changes%20may%20be%20an%20adjustment.%20But%20there%20are%20ways%20to%20make%20a%20more%20rigid%20structure%20tolerable%2C%20according%20to%20Jennifer%20Moss%2C%20a%20workplace%20strategist%20and%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BWhy%20Are%20We%20Here%3F.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20suggests%20building%20friendships%20with%20colleagues%20or%20finding%20a%20way%20to%20take%20that%2030-minute%20walk%20to%20create%20some%20balance.%20Spending%20time%20planning%20out%20your%20next%20career%20steps%20can%20also%20be%20helpful%2C%20she%20said%2C%20so%20you%20know%20where%20you%20want%20to%20go%20%E2%80%94%20and%20what%20matters%20most.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20are%20going%20to%20stay%20there%2C%20you%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20you%20are%20doing%20everything%20in%20your%20power%20to%20make%20it%20as%20enjoyable%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Moss.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20long%20life%2C%20and%20work%20plays%20a%20big%20role%20in%20our%20lifespan%20and%20our%20long-term%20health.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20who%20are%20seeking%20a%20different%20company%20culture%2C%20it%20may%20be%20time%20to%20start%20job%20hunting.%20But%20you%20may%20need%20to%20be%20flexible%2C%20said%20Escalera.%20If%20you're%20looking%20to%20work%20remotely%2C%20for%20example%2C%20consider%20what%20you%20might%20be%20willing%20to%20give%20up%2C%20such%20as%20higher%20pay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20you%20willing%20to%20adjust%20in%20order%20to%20receive%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20may%20not%20be%20a%20good%20time%20to%20call%20it%20quits%20without%20a%20plan.%20In%20July%2C%20the%20US%20economy%20added%20just%2073%2C000%20jobs%2C%20well%20below%20the%20106%2C000%20that%20economists%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20it%20might%20be%20time%20to%20start%20looking%20for%20new%20opportunities%2C%20knowing%20it%20might%20take%20longer%20to%20find%20something.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20walk%20out%20right%20now.%20The%20job%20market%20is%20not%20nice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Goodall%2C%20whose%20business%20is%20called%20The%20Job%20Chick.%20%26quot%3BYou've%20got%20to%20play%20the%20game%2C%20unfortunately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20your%20company's%20changing%20culture%3F%20Contact%20reporters%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asneedleman%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Esneedleman%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Atparadis%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Etparadis%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fembed.typeform.com%2Fnext%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20data-tf-live%3D%5C%2201K1TWYPCPJRA66C99YPG5MMTA%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5dbe5c4-7dec-41e0-a25b-eba557730877%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-hardcore-era-employee-changes-att-memo-2025-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754343371000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6