t%20sleepers%20like%20my%20husband.%20I%2C%20however%2C%20sleep%20cold%20and%20prefer%20the%20softer%2C%20warmer%20texture%20of%20cotton%20or%20sateen%20fabric.%20Brooklinen's%20newly%20upgraded%20Washed%20European%20Linen%20Sheets%20promised%20a%20lived-in%20feel%20that%20only%20got%20softer%20with%20each%20wash%2C%20so%20we%20decided%20to%20give%20them%20a%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20that%20struck%20me%20about%20these%20sheets%20was%20the%20color%20choices.%20I'm%20a%20sucker%20for%20stripes%2C%20so%20I%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20picking%20from%20the%2016%20different%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22brooklinen%20washed%20european%20linen%20sheet%20set%20packaging%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6891094b3d5881a51c1e9285%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Brooklinen%20Sheets%20ship%20quickly%20and%20arrived%20with%20a%20cardboard%20sleeve%20and%20in%20plastic.%20There%20is%20no%20fabric%20dust%20bag.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Brooklinen%20sheets%20were%20delivered%20quickly%20and%20felt%20soft%20to%20the%20touch%20immediately%20upon%20opening.%20I%20had%20never%20slept%20on%20linen%20sheets%20prior%2C%20but%20these%20were%20nothing%20like%20the%20scratchy%2C%20stiff%20fabric%20I%20had%20imagined.%20They%20were%20actually%20quite%20smooth%20and%20breathable%2C%20like%20a%20luxurious%20version%20of%20your%20favorite%20worn-in%20T-shirt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20these%20sheets%20were%20definitely%20on%20the%20lighter%20side%2C%20compared%20to%20a%20flannel%20or%20heavier%20cotton%2C%20they%20had%20a%20nice%20weight%20to%20them%20that%20felt%20durable%20and%20strong.%20Something%20that%20I%20was%20able%20to%20confirm%20after%20a%20few%20washes.%20Pills%20and%20nags%20were%20nonexistent%20until%20about%20the%20seventh%20wash%2C%20and%20even%20then%2C%20the