sswork%20out%20of%20making%20the%20bed.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20other%20issue%20I%20had%20was%20with%20the%20size%20of%20the%20fitted%20sheets.%20We%20have%20a%20decently%20thick%20mattress%20topper%20on%20our%20queen-sized%20bed%2C%20and%20the%2015-inch%20pockets%20just%20barely%20cover%20it%20all.%20We've%20had%20to%20get%20inventive%20with%20sheet%20clips%20and%20suspenders%20to%20keep%20it%20from%20riding%20up.%20It's%20not%20a%20dealbreaker%2C%20but%20definitely%20something%20to%20be%20aware%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I%20highly%20recommend%20Brooklinen's%20linen%20sheets%20for%20anyone%2C%20especially%20couples%20with%20differing%20temperature%20preferences%2C%20looking%20to%20upgrade%20their%20bedding%20game.%20But%20at%20over%20%24300%20a%20set%2C%20I%20advise%20waiting%20for%20a%20sale%2C%20as%20I've%20seen%20this%20sheet%20set%20discounted%20for%20as%20much%20as%2030%25%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c07f0bff-9697-425f-a37d-cbc5b1cb4286%5C%22%3ECare%20requirements%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%20these%20linen%20sheets%20are%20machine%20washable%20and%20can%20be%20tossed%20in%20with%20like%20colors.%20Brooklinen%20recommends%20washing%20them%20in%20cold%20water%20and%20tumble%20drying%20them%20on%20a%20low%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I've%20had%20no%20bleeding%20or%20excessive%20pilling%20after%20washing%20my%20sheets%2C%20I%20do%20wish%20I%20had%20washed%20them%20before%20our%20first%20night%20sleeping%20in%20them%2C%20as%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20loose%20fibers%20that%20came%20off%20during%20the%20first%20wash.%20Linen%20is%20known%20to%20soften%20up%20overtime%20as%20you%20wash%20them%2C%20which%20can%20help%20with%20the%20initial%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22258dcb05-664a-482d-b36c-e52e6abaea7e%5C%22%3E365-day%20trial%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EBrooklinen%20offers%20a%20365-day%20return%20policy%20and%20an%20additional%20yearlong