uld%20either%20embrace%20AI%20or%20leave%20the%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20candid%20statement%2C%20part%20of%20a%20blog%20post%20titled%20%26quot%3BDevelopers%2C%20Reinvented%2C%26quot%3B%20underscores%20the%20dramatic%20transformation%20underway%20in%20software%20development%2C%20a%20shift%20not%20just%20in%20how%20code%20is%20written%2C%20but%20in%20the%20very%20nature%20of%20what%20it%20means%20to%20be%20a%20developer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20blog%20drew%20from%20interviews%20with%2022%20developers%20already%20deeply%20integrating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-coding-agents-adoption-top-tools-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20their%20workflows.%20Their%20experiences%20paint%20a%20clear%20picture%3A%20AI%20isn't%20a%20distant%20future%2C%20it's%20a%20present%20necessity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEither%20you%20have%20to%20embrace%20the%20Al%2C%20or%20you%20get%20out%20of%20your%20career%2C%26quot%3B%20Dohmke%20wrote%2C%20citing%20one%20of%20the%20developers%20who%20GitHub%20interviewed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20latest%20example%20of%20a%20strange%20marketing%20strategy%20by%20AI%20companies.%20Instead%20of%20selling%20products%20based%20on%20helpful%20features%20and%20letting%20users%20decide%2C%20executives%20often%20deploy%20scare%20tactics%20that%20essentially%20warn%20people%20they%20will%20become%20obsolete%20if%20they%20don't%20get%20on%20the%20AI%20bandwagon.%20For%20instance%2C%20Julia%20Liuson%2C%20another%20executive%20at%20Microsoft%2C%20which%20owns%20GitHub%2C%20recently%20warned%20employees%20that%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-internal-memo-using-ai-no-longer-optional-github-copilot-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eusing%20AI%20is%20no%20longer%20optional%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c4a1d70e-cd0f-4c07-b515-ef3679efbe70%5C%22%3EFrom%20skeptics%20to%20strategists%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDohmke%20said%20developers%20who%20initially%20dismissed%20tools%20such%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-internal-memo-using-ai-no-longer-optional-github-copilot-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGitHub%20Copilot%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20gimmicks%20now%20see%20them%20as%20indispensable%20collaborators.%20Through%20trial%20and%20error%2C%20these%20people%20have%20evolved%20from%20skeptics%20to%20AI%20strategists%2C%20learning%20to%20delegate%20coding%20tasks%20to%20AI%20agents%20and%20focusing%20their%20efforts%20on%20context%20design%2C%20prompt%20engineering%2C%20and%20verification%2C%20the%20CEO%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20no%20marginal%20change.%20Developers%20at%20the%20leading%20edge%20of%20this%20transition%20report%20that%20their%20roles%20have%20shifted%20from%20writing%20code%20to%20architecting%20and%20auditing%20the%20code%20generated%20by%20AI.%20They%20speak%20of%20themselves%20not%20as%20coders%2C%20but%20as%20%26quot%3Bcode%20enablers%26quot%3B%20or%20even%20%26quot%3Bcreative%20directors%20of%20code%2C%26quot%3B%20Dohmke%20wrote%20in%20his%20blog.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229619c951-1de9-4e63-af06-11131103fdd0%5C%22%3ERedefining%20developer%20value%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20argued%20that%20this%20transformation%20does%20not%20diminish%20developers'%20value%2C%20but%20redefines%20it.%20Those%20who%20adopt%20AI%20tools%20early%20gain%20leverage%2C%20not%20redundancy.%20The%20blog%20highlights%20a%20major%20mindset%20shift%3A%20instead%20of%20optimizing%20solely%20for%20speed%20or%20efficiency%2C%20developers%20are%20using%20AI%20to%20raise%20the%20ambition%20of%20what's%20possible%2C%20Dohmke%20wrote%2C%20while%20noting%20that%20complex%2C%20large-scale%20refactoring%20tasks%20or%20multi-agent%20feature%20builds%20that%20once%20seemed%20out%20of%20reach%20are%20now%20achievable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20reframing%20comes%20with%20a%20career%20challenge%3A%20adapt%20or%20risk%20becoming%20obsolete.%20As%20AI%20rapidly%20advances%20toward%20automating%20up%20to%2090%25%20of%20code%20writing%20%E2%80%94%20a%20timeline%20developers%20estimate%20could%20arrive%20within%20just%20two%20to%20five%20years%20%E2%80%94%20the%20skills%20that%20will%20matter%20most%20include%20system%20design%2C%20AI%20fluency%2C%20delegation%2C%20and%20quality%20assurance%2C%20he%20predicted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20software%20developer%20role%20is%20set%20on%20a%20path%20of%20significant%20change.%20Not%20everyone%20will%20want%20to%20make%20the%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BManaging%20agents%20to%20achieve%20outcomes%20may%20sound%20unfulfilling%20to%20many%2C%20although%20we%20argue%20that's%20what%20developers%20have%20been%20doing%20on%20a%20lower%20level%20of%20abstraction%2C%20managing%20their%20computers%20via%20programming%20languages%20to%20achieve%20outcomes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHumans%20are%20often%20reluctant%20to%20change%2C%20and%20Dohmke%20ended%20his%20blog%20by%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20okay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20clear%20is%20that%20the%20CEO%20thinks%20these%20humans%20should%20seek%20another%20profession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-6-figures-plumbing-trades-support-family-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eplumbing%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESign%20up%20for%20BI's%20Tech%20Memo%20newsletter%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubscription%2Fnewsletter%2Ftech-memo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E.%20Reach%20out%20to%20me%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabarr%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabarr%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3