o%20discuss%20different%20factors%20impacting%20today's%20procurement%20departments%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20data%20and%20AI%20play%20a%20role%20in%20its%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeakers%20included%20Sandhya%20Dhir%2C%20head%20of%20new%20solution%20development%20at%20Amazon%20Business%3B%20Paula%20Glickenhaus%2C%20chief%20procurement%20officer%20at%20Bristol%20Myers%20Squibb%3B%20and%20Sheila%20Gundersen%2C%20managing%20director%20of%20global%20procurement%20and%20sourcing%20at%20SMBC%20Americas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20moderated%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fshefali-kapadia%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShefali%20Kapadia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20contributor%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20surprisingly%2C%20all%20panelists%20agreed%20that%20AI%20is%20playing%20a%20role%20in%20how%20procurement%20departments%20are%20servicing%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20is%20here%20to%20stay%2C%26quot%3B%20Bristol%20Myers%20Squibb's%20Glickenhaus%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%20year%2C%20there's%20been%20a%20rapid%20surge%20of%20AI%20solutions%20and%20also%20an%20interest%20from%20stakeholders%20to%20understand%20how%20procurement%20can%20use%20AI%20to%20differentiate%20how%20we%20service%20the%20business%2C%20how%20we%20give%20them%20faster%20solutions%2C%20how%20we%20provide%20analytics%20forward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDhir%20said%20one%20of%20the%20opportunities%20she%20sees%20for%20AI%20in%20procurement%20is%20to%20help%20with%20inefficient%20manual%20workflows%20or%20approval%20chains%20that%20result%20in%20bottlenecks%20and%20oversight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20can%20auto%20adapt%20to%2C%20or%20learn%2C%20each%20client's%20data%20and%20assign%20tasks%20within%20a%20workflow%20based%20on%20capacity%20or%20priority%20and%20internal%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20Amazon%20Business'%20Dhir%20said.%20%26quot%3BWorkflows%20can%20automatically%20adapt%20based%20on%20user%20metrics%20and%20potential%20inefficiencies.%20And%20then%20on%20top%20of%20that%2C%20a%20solution%20can%20also%20leverage%20Gen%20AI%20and%20create%20guidance%20for%20resolutions%20such%20as%20recommendations%20of%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20when%20she's%20doing%20a%20task%20more%20than%20once%2C%20that's%20when%20she%20starts%20looking%20for%20AI%20solutions.%20She%20also%20said%20it's%20important%20to%20build%20in%20additional%20time%20at%20first%20when%20establishing%20an%20AI%20workflow.%20%26quot%3BExpect%20it%20to%20take%20longer%20at%20first%20as%20you%20figure%20out%20the%20right%20prompts%20or%20the%20right%20tool%20or%20even%20create%20the%20mechanism%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhir%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d1314a41-8c29-4914-a376-1d6f39630f16%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20reactive%20response%20to%20proactive%20planning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETraditionally%2C%20procurement%20has%20focused%20on%20risk%20and%20reactive%20planning%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20supplier%20relationships%2C%20but%20that%20is%20shifting%2C%20Gundersen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20definitely%20transitioned%20to%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20be%20more%20proactive%2C%20what%20tools%20and%20capabilities%20there%20are%E2%80%94%20whether%20it's%20from%20AI%20and%2For%20other%20ongoing%20monitoring%20tools%2C%26quot%3B%20Gunderson%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20definitely%20being%20able%20to%20build%20that%20into%20the%20supply%20chain%20management%2C%20risk%20management%20function%20is%20important.%20I%20think%20that's%20where%20everybody%20is%20moving%20and%20trending.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20big%20part%20of%20that%20transition%20is%20due%20to%20the%20data%20that%20is%20available%20to%20collect%20and%20analyze%2C%20SMBC's%20Glickenhaus%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGlickenhaus%20cited%20recent%20earthquakes%20and%20tsunamis%20as%20an%20example%20of%20how%20things%20have%20shifted.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20they%20would%20need%20hours