%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F387261%2Fsenior-citizens-travel-story-childhood-friendships-girls-trip-tourism-adventure%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20meaningful%20bonds%20%3C%2Fa%3Eoften%20begin%20in%20the%20ordinary.%20As%20we%20grow%20older%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20loud%20declarations%2C%20but%20the%20soft%2C%20steady%20presence%20of%20a%20friend%20that%20often%20makes%20all%20the%20difference.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754055000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T233342.337-1753985156.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D479281%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Friendships%20don%E2%80%99t%20always%20begin%20with%20a%20dramatic%20story.%20Sometimes%2C%20they%20grow%20quietly%20on%20dance%20floors%2C%20badminton%20courts%2C%20or%20through%20a%20podcast%20mic.%20This%20Friendship%20Day%2C%20we%20celebrate%20stories%20of%20people%20whose%20strongest%20bonds%20were%20formed%20through%20creativity%2C%20compassion%2C%20and%20shared%20life%20moments.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Saumya%20Singh%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F479281%2Freal-friendship-stories-dance-art-cubbon-park-bengaluru-graphic-designing%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Family%20Resurrected%20Their%20300-YO%20Ancestral%20Palace%20Into%20a%20Glorious%20Heritage%20Hotel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20feature%20were%20conducted%20in%202024.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20palace%20was%20overgrown%20with%20brambles%3B%20the%20manor%20barely%20visible%20through%20the%20forests%20that%20threatened%20to%20suffocate%20it.%20Even%20the%20highest%20points%20of%20the%20castle%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20spared.%20Wild%20plants%20held%20the%20towers%20in%20a%20vice-like%20grip.%20In%20some%20places%2C%20the%20roof%20had%20crumbled%3B%20in%20others%20it%20had%20shattered%2C%20closing%20off%20entrances%20and%20exits.%20No%20one%20knew%20for%20sure%20what%20the%20house%20held%20within%20it.%20Were%20there%20wild%20beasts%20lurking%20inside%3F%20Or%20something%20more%20ferocious%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20much%20as%20it%20sounds%20like%20an%20excerpt%20from%20one%20of%20Grimm%E2%80%99s%20Fairy%20Tales%2C%20the%20incident%20is%20a%20real-life%20scene%20that%20awaited%20Pallab%20Roy%20(60)%20and%20his%20family%20when%20they%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F310006%2Froyal-sisters-duo-akshita-mrinalika-the-belgadia-palace-boutique-hotel-odisha-sustainable-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erevisited%20their%20ancestral%20palace%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Kasim%20Bazar%2C%20Murshidabad%2C%20West%20Bengal.%20The%20300-year-old%20architecture%20had%20fallen%20into%20a%20state%20of%20despair%20since%20its%20last%20occupant%2C%20Pallab%E2%80%99s%20grandfather%20Raja%20Kamalaranjan%20Roy%2C%20passed%20away%20in%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPallab%20has%20my%20unwavering%20attention%20as%20he%20narrates%20his%20story%2C%20a%20tale%20that%20takes%20me%20back%20to%20an%20Enid%20Blyton%20adventure.%20He%2C%20along%20with%20his%20parents%20Prosanta%20Kumar%20and%20Supriya%20Roy%2C%20his%20wife%20Sudeshna%2C%20his%20son%20Saurav%2C%20and%20his%20daughter-in-law%20Priya%2C%20would%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20take%20upon%20them%20the%20arduous%20task%20of%20restoring%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20to%20its%20former%20glory.%20The%20goal%20was%20to%20turn%20this%20spectral%20ruin%20into%20a%20liveable%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Operation%20clean-up%E2%80%99%3A%20Battling%20snakes%20and%20lizards%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20approaching%20one%20room%20at%20a%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20says%20as%20he%20recalls%20the%20renovation%20process.%20However%2C%20it%20was%20only%20when%20%E2%80%98operation%20clean-up%E2%80%99%20commenced%20that%20the%20family%20could%20ascertain%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20devastation.%20The%20years%20of%20isolation%20had%20taken%20a%20toll%20on%20the%20royal%20beauty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInsects%2C%20five-inch%20thick%20layers%20of%20dust%20and%20crumbling%20roofs%20marred%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20efforts%20to%20restore%20what%20had%20once%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F341653%2Funique-homestay-in-goa-maharashtra-sawantwadi-palace-hotel-run-by-royal-family-sawant-bhonsle%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esymbol%20of%20grandeur%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20place%20was%20infested%20with%20snakes%20and%20monitor%20lizards%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20exclaims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20is%20an%2018th%20century%20marvel%20in%20Murshidabad%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1726572982-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366171%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20is%20an%2018th-century%20marvel%20in%20Murshidabad.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1-1726573107.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20300-year-old%20palace%20was%20in%20a%20state%20of%20disrepair%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Raja%20Kamalaranjan%20Roy%20in%201993%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1-1726573107.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1-1726573107-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1-1726573107-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1-1726573107-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-1-1726573107-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366173%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20300-year-old%20palace%20was%20in%20a%20state%20of%20disrepair%20after%20the%20death%20of%20Raja%20Kamalaranjan%20Roy%20in%201993.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20family%20scoured%20the%20rooms%20of%20the%20ancestral%20palace%2C%20attempting%20to%20identify%20the%20degree%20of%20cleaning%20each%20required%2C%20they%20were%20met%20with%20more%20surprises%2C%20or%20rather%20shocks.%20%E2%80%9CSome%20rooms%E2%80%99%20arches%20were%20blocked%20with%20bricks.%20When%20we%20managed%20to%20get%20into%20the%20rooms%2C%20we%20noticed%20that%20the%20doors%20and%20windows%20had%20vanished.%20We%20guessed%20that%20they%20had%20been%20vandalised%20or%20eaten%20by%20termites.%20Even%20some%20of%20the%20supporting%20beams%20were%20missing%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20recalls.%20The%20cleaning%20spree%20went%20on%20for%20years%2C%20yielding%20three%20rooms%20that%20were%20deemed%20fit%20to%20live%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20family%20decided%20to%20turn%20the%20ancestral%20palace%20into%20a%20guesthouse.%20However%2C%20Pallab%20explains%20that%20the%20plan%20flopped%20as%20social%20media%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20as%20popular%20back%20then%20and%20most%20people%E2%80%99s%20first%20choice%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20a%20guest%20house.%20It%20seemed%20like%20the%2018th-century%20palace%20would%20remain%20desolate.%20Unable%20to%20watch%20their%20ancestral%20pride%20meet%20such%20a%20fate%2C%20the%20Roy%20family%20decided%20to%20rebuild%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332940%2Fdevpur-royal-homestay-darbargadh-in-kutch-jadeja-family-runs-farmstay-cbse-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroyal%20residence%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20soon%20become%20a%20heritage%20hotel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Buckingham%20of%20India%E2%80%99%3A%20Reviving%20a%20lost%20legacy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20heyday%2C%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20would%20have%20earned%20the%20%E2%80%98Buckingham%20of%20India%E2%80%99%20moniker.%20Explaining%20the%20comparison%2C%20Pallab%20shares%20that%20the%20palace%E2%80%99s%20functioning%20was%20in%20tune%20with%20colonial%20times%20and%20its%20practices%20mirrored%20those%20at%20Buckingham%20Palace%20in%20England.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20British%20Government%20had%20a%20system%20of%20administering%20estates%20through%20the%20Court%20of%20Wards%20if%20the%20person%20in%20power%20was%20a%20minor%20and%20the%20guardian%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20present.%20Across%20the%2010%20generations%20of%20our%20family%2C%20three%20generations%20have%20seen%20their%20owners%20die%20young.%20And%20so%2C%20for%20almost%2045%20years%2C%20the%20British%20Government%20administered%20the%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20grandfather%20%E2%80%93%20who%20lost%20his%20father%20at%20the%20age%20of%20six%20months%20%E2%80%93%20was%20brought%20up%20by%20a%20British%20governess%20for%20six%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-3-1726573323.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20boasts%2014%20rooms%20which%20can%20accommodate%20a%20total%20of%2040%20guests%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-3-1726573323.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-3-1726573323-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-3-1726573323-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-3-1726573323-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcossimbazar-palace-in-india-3-1726573323-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366177%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20of%20the%20Roys%20(Rajbari)%20boasts%2014%20rooms%20which%20can%20accommodate%20a%20total%20of%2040%20guests.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20delve%20further%20into%20history%2C%20Pallab%20draws%20attention%20to%20the%20notable%20parallels%20between%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%E2%80%99s%20functions%20and%20those%20of%20the%20palaces%20in%20England.%20%E2%80%9CAround%201924%2C%20the%20house%20had%20200%20guards.%20There%20was%20also%20the%20%E2%80%98Changing%20of%20the%20Guard%E2%80%99%20ceremony%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F48468%2Flieutenant-colonel-sophia-qureshi-indian-army%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary%20drills%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20were%2034%20gardeners%2C%20innumerable%20staff%20and%20nine%20functioning%20kitchens.%E2%80%9D%20He%20laughs%20as%20he%20recounts%20the%20famous%20tea%20parties%20held%20at%20Cossimbazar%20Palace.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20crockery%20and%20cutlery%20for%20these%20were%20imported%20from%20England!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20in%201947%2C%20as%20India%20got%20freedom%2C%20and%20the%20estate%20system%20was%20abolished%20soon%20after%2C%20the%20fate%20of%20Cossimbazar%20Palace%20took%20a%20drastic%20turn.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FVZaaCzClgxA%3Fsi%3D1WO9zmnnvPyi5MQ3%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20assets%20in%20our%20family%20were%20self-earned%20over%2010%20generations%3B%20they%20were%20not%20grants%20from%20the%20Government.%20But%20everything%20went%20away%20without%20a%20single%20%3Cem%3Epaisa%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Indian%20currency%20denomination)%3B%20they%20were%20auctioned.%20I%20have%20heard%20stories%20of%20how%20everything%20vanished%20overnight%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pallab%20laments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CM