aves%2C%20but%20now%20she%20was%20managing%20an%20FPO%20that%20empowered%20farmers.%20Her%20story%20gave%20me%20hope%20that%20with%20the%20right%20resources%2C%20anybody%20can%20rise%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20create%20something%20that%20went%20beyond%20just%20supporting%20farmers.%20I%20wanted%20them%20to%20have%20a%20stake%20in%20the%20entire%20process%2C%20from%20cultivation%20to%20sales%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20young%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20fellowship%2C%20he%20returned%20to%20his%20hometown%20where%20he%20discussed%20his%20desire%20to%20make%20a%20difference%20with%20his%20schoolmates%2C%20Rohit%20Negi%20and%20Mohit%20Rana.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSince%20college%2C%20we%20used%20to%20talk%20about%20doing%20business%20together.%20Whenever%20we%20saw%20farmers%20working%20so%20hard%2C%20we%20thought%20about%20how%20they%20struggle%20to%20provide%20for%20their%20families%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20says%20Mohit%2C%20who%20has%20an%20engineering%20background%20and%20was%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20working%20as%20a%20civil%20engineer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three%20friends%20got%20together%20to%20take%20the%20entrepreneurial%20plunge%20and%20founded%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20in%202021.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20inspiration%20to%20join%20this%20venture%20stemmed%20from%20a%20deep%20desire%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F254622%2Flenovo-technology-agastya-international-meghshala-door-step-school-technoserve-medha-social-impact-innovation-oniline-education-c24%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehelp%20people%20in%20rural%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20want%20to%20stay%20with%20their%20families%20while%20earning%20a%20livelihood.%20I%20wanted%20to%20empower%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Rohit%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20sales%20and%20operations%2C%20Mohit%2C%20who%20quit%20his%20job%20to%20co-found%20the%20venture%2C%20focused%20on%20sourcing%20raw%20materials%20and%20quality%20control.%20Together%2C%20they%20created%20a%20model%20they%20believed%20could%20transform%20rural%20livelihoods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20path%20towards%20empowering%20farmers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20where%20we%20received%20an%20initial%20grant%20of%20Rs%203%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20says.%20Their%20goal%20was%20to%20buy%20produce%20directly%20from%20farmers%20and%20offer%20them%20better%20prices.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20procured%20millets%20from%20farmers%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20sold%20them%20to%20buyers%20in%20southern%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeart%20in%20Hills%20operated%20in%20Uttarakhand%20by%20procuring%20millets%20directly%20from%20local%20farmers%2C%20offering%20them%2010-15%25%20higher%20prices%20than%20the%20market%20rate%20as%20an%20incentive%20for%20their%20quality%20produce.%20The%20company%20provided%20primary%20processing%20services%2C%20including%20grading%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20cleaning%20of%20the%20millets%2C%20before%20selling%20them%20to%20bulk%20clients%20down%20south.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%202020%20and%202021%2C%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20helped%20me%20earn%20approximately%20Rs%204%20lakh.%20I%20could%20repay%20my%20loans%20and%20purchase%20essentials%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Subdei%20(78)%2C%20from%20Luthiyag%20village%2C%20Rudraprayag%20district.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20traders%20would%20buy%20from%20me%20but%20didn%E2%80%99t%20pay%20me%20fairly.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20capable%20enough%20to%20run%20my%20business%2C%20trading%20pulses%20and%20millets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114823.675-1754029136.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Foreka%20aims%20to%20train%20women%20farmers%20so%20they%20can%20help%20increase%20the%20sales%20of%20cold-pressed%20oils%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114823.675-1754029136.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114823.675-1754029136-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114823.675-1754029136-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114823.675-1754029136-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114823.675-1754029136-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-479456%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EForeka%20aims%20to%20train%20women%20farmers%20so%20they%20can%20help%20increase%20the%20sales%20of%20cold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20running%20a%20large-scale%20venture%20was%20not%20easy.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20traders%20felt%20threatened%20by%20our%20model.%20They%20were%20used%20to%20controlling%20the%20market%2C%20but%20we%20believed%20in%20the%20power%20of%20direct%20trade%2C%E2%80%9D%20Satyam%20says.%20Despite%20their%20venture%20causing%20some%20tension%20in%20the%20local%20markets%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20pressed%20on.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20soon%20the%20young%20entrepreneur%20realised%20that%20offering%20higher%20incentives%20to%20farmers%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20enough%20to%20sustain%20long-term%20growth.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20business%20became%20increasingly%20seasonal%2C%20with%20supply%20chain%20challenges%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20maintain%20consistent%20operations.%20So%2C%20we%20had%20to%20stop%20our%20operations%20in%20Uttarakhand%20and%20come%20up%20with%20a%20better%20approach%20to%20expand%20our%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20cold-pressed%20oil%20brand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20second%20COVID-19%20wave%2C%20he%20and%20his%20team%20noticed%20an%20increasing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328846%2Fsibi-manivannan-runs-gramiya-cold-pressed-oils-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edemand%20for%20cold-pressed%20oils%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20insight%20led%20them%20to%20pivot%20their%20business%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202022%2C%20the%20Heart%20in%20Hills%20team%20ventured%20into%20the%20cold-pressed%20oil%20market%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20Foreka%20in%20Rajasthan.%20This%20expansion%20was%20made%20possible%20by%20the%20support%20Satyam%20received%20in%20November%202020%2C%20when%20he%20was%20awarded%20a%20prestigious%20fellowship%20from%20The%20Buddha%20Institute%2C%20founded%20by%20Ved%20Arya%2C%20an%20alumnus%20of%20IIM%20Ahmedabad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Buddha%20Institute%20provided%20us%20with%20a%20generous%20grant%20of%20Rs%2022%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares%2C%20which%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20enabling%20the%20team%20to%20scale%20their%20operations.%20Their%20research%20into%20the%20region%20highlighted%20a%20high%20rate%20of%20outmigration%2C%20presenting%20an%20opportunity%20to%20create%20local%20employment.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20exceptional%20quality%20of%20mustard%20seeds%20in%20the%20area%20made%20it%20an%20ideal%20location%20for%20their%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20partnered%20with%20NGOs%20like%20SRIJAN%20to%20establish%20a%20value%20chain%20for%20farming%2C%20offering%20farmers%20better%20prices%20and%20resources%20to%20test%20seed%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20supporting%20farmers%20directly%2C%20we%20ensured%20fair%20prices%20and%20sustainable%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satyam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%20The%20setup%20includes%20cold-pressed%20machines%20owned%20by%20the%20farmers%2C%20while%20Foreka%20works%20on%20a%20co-profit%20model%2C%20sharing%2050%25%20of%20the%20profits%20after%20covering%20costs.%20Partnering%20with%20two%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisations%20(FPOs)%2C%20one%20near%20Jhansi%20and%20the%20other%20in%20the%20Chambal%20Valley%2C%20Foreka%20sources%20groundnuts%2C%20processes%20them%2C%20and%20sells%20groundnut%20oil.%20The%20model%20helps%20reduce%20outmigration%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F311715%2Fbengaluru-social-impact-startup-mikro-grafeio-creates-employment-in-tier-ii-and-iii-indian-cities%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecreate%20local%20employment%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Their%20breakthrough%20came%20with%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20processing%20unit%20in%20Hindaun%2C%20Karauli%20district%2C%20Rajasthan.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-1754029024-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-01T114643.416-17540